==English==

===Noun Phrase===
'''bovine spongiform encephalopathy'''

A fatal, neurodegenerative disease of cattle, which is transmissable to humans through misshaped [[prion]] proteins, caused by eating infected [[tissue]]s.  Transmission is usually epedemic and the [[disease]] originated from the [[United Kingdom]].  Abbreviation: [[BSE]].

